00:39:58,599 --> 00:40:04,679
[SPEAKER_00] tako da ne bi ja rekao da pravi muškarac ne plaće

1255
00:40:04,679 --> 00:40:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] ili da nike ne bi trebalo plakat,

1256
00:40:06,539 --> 00:40:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno može oni za plakat,

1257
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] ali recimo za prave stvari,

1258
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] nekad o gadinamu gubi ili

1259
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] kad se zatvore birtije zbog korona,

1260
00:40:20,579 --> 00:40:23,780
[SPEAKER_00] znači ako je neki pravi opravdan razlog,

1261
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:25,219
[SPEAKER_00] onda naravno, znači nema problema.

1262
00:40:25,219 --> 00:40:28,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, rođenje djeteta čovje će...

1263
00:40:28,719 --> 00:40:29,179
[SPEAKER_01] Plaći.

1264
00:40:29,179 --> 00:40:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] Plaći, plaći.

1265
00:40:30,579 --> 00:40:30,860
[SPEAKER_01] Udri.

1266
00:40:30,860 --> 00:40:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, a klečanje?

1267
00:40:36,539 --> 00:40:40,340
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, da, zašto ne?

1268
00:40:40,340 --> 00:40:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ne?

1269
00:40:41,019 --> 00:40:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je to jako dobar pokazati drugima.

1270
00:40:44,460 --> 00:40:49,159
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, evo sad baš lazi na pamet jedna priča,

1271
00:40:49,159 --> 00:40:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno svećanstva Damira Stojića.

1272
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:56,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, njemu je narasao taj žar da služi u crkvi,

1273
00:40:56,719 --> 00:41:01,139
[SPEAKER_00] da postane svećenik i da uđe u dublju modu kada je vidio svog oca

1274
00:41:01,139 --> 00:41:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] kako kleči, kada moli, kako kleči u crkvi.

1275
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, to je nešto jako, jako poticajno.

1276
00:41:10,980 --> 00:41:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] Izbilja pokazuje tu neku poniznost,

1277
00:41:17,159 --> 00:41:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] taj neki žar i tu neku žeć za Bogom.

1278
00:41:23,739 --> 00:41:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, tu se pokazuje da možda ta osoba nije savršen otac,

1279
00:41:30,340 --> 00:41:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali ona zapravo pokazuje ako pogriješi,

1280
00:41:33,039 --> 00:41:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] ko je taj savršen otac.

1281
00:41:35,159 --> 00:41:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] na koga se to djete može ugledati,

1282
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] po uzdati ako taj otac pogriješi.

1283
00:41:40,159 --> 00:41:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mnoga djeca odrastaju mislići da su njihovi očevi bogovi.

1284
00:41:46,380 --> 00:41:49,679
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda kada pogriješe, ona im se sruši slika otca.

1285
00:41:49,679 --> 00:41:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali recimo, ako njihov otac kleči,

1286
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] čime pokazuje da on može i pogriješiti,

1287
00:41:55,840 --> 00:41:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] da je slab, da je potrebit milosti,

1288
00:41:58,500 --> 00:42:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] onda je tu drugačiji odnos prema otcu,

1289
00:42:02,599 --> 00:42:09,880
[SPEAKER_00] prema molitvi, prema sve ono što crkva predstavlja

1290
00:42:09,880 --> 00:42:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] i što se traži od jednog katoličkog muškarca.

1291
00:42:12,519 --> 00:42:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da klečanje i plakanje nije uopće nešto diskutabilno.

1292
00:42:21,460 --> 00:42:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je nešto i vrlo pozitivno.

1293
00:42:24,460 --> 00:42:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se naravno opet kleči za pravu stvar.

1294
00:42:27,199 --> 00:42:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ne opet, ako njih nam izgubi,

1295
00:42:30,079 --> 00:42:33,280
[SPEAKER_00] pa opet kleknemo, pa plačemo ili ne znam,

1296
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] plećemo pred birtijom da se otvori ili tako nešto.

1297
00:42:36,099 --> 00:42:41,980
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ovo što si spomenuo, svakako djeca udrastaju,

1298
00:42:41,980 --> 00:42:46,760
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno djete u svome otcu i svojoj majci gleda Boga

1299
00:42:46,760 --> 00:42:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] i gleda sliku Boga.

1300
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:50,880
[SPEAKER_01] A to je onda ono s početka što si govorio,

1301
00:42:50,880 --> 00:42:57,699
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, kad jedno djete nema otca ili je nekakva kritična,

1302
00:42:57,699 --> 00:43:01,699
[SPEAKER_01] da tako kažemo, uloga otca ili da otac negdje zakaže,

1303
00:43:01,699 --> 00:43:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] a puno toga možemo zakazati.

1304
00:43:04,800 --> 00:43:07,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ja i kao otac to svaki dan vidim,

1305
00:43:07,559 --> 00:43:13,019
[SPEAKER_01] da se možemo ne ono sedam puta,

1306
00:43:13,019 --> 00:43:17,860
[SPEAKER_01] nego sedam deset puta sedam pogrešaka u danu napraviti

1307
00:43:17,860 --> 00:43:19,900
[SPEAKER_01] i u odnosu, i u razgovoru,

1308
00:43:19,900 --> 00:43:23,219
[SPEAKER_01] i u reagiranju, puno toga.

1309
00:43:24,300 --> 00:43:27,079
[SPEAKER_01] Onda stvarno možeš samo to napraviti.

1310
00:43:27,079 --> 00:43:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš na kraju dana, evo sada kad ja završim ovaj live s tobom,

1311
00:43:31,000 --> 00:43:35,500
[SPEAKER_01] možeš lijepo sjesti u svoju sobu,

1312
00:43:35,500 --> 00:43:38,719
[SPEAKER_01] kleknuti u svoju sobu pred Bogom i reći,

1313
00:43:38,719 --> 00:43:40,460
[SPEAKER_01] evo Bože, ja sam učinio,

1314
00:43:40,460 --> 00:43:42,900
[SPEAKER_01] ili sam se barem potrudio, ako jesi.

1315
00:43:42,900 --> 00:43:47,579
[SPEAKER_01] Potrudio sam se biti najbolji što sam mogao biti,

1316
00:43:47,579 --> 00:43:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] a tamo gdje sam ja stao,

1317
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] ti nadopuni, ti nastavi,

1318
00:43:51,559 --> 00:43:53,519
[SPEAKER_01] ti promijeni,

1319
00:43:53,900 --> 00:43:54,780
[SPEAKER_01] ti ispravi.

1320
00:43:54,780 --> 00:43:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] To je baš,

1321
00:43:56,500 --> 00:43:57,840
[SPEAKER_01] i to je meni,

1322
00:43:57,840 --> 00:44:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] meni, kao katoličkom muškarcu i mužu,

1323
00:44:01,099 --> 00:44:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] je to jedna velika utjeha.

1324
00:44:03,340 --> 00:44:07,480
[SPEAKER_01] To je meni osobno jedna velika utjeha.

1325
00:44:07,480 --> 00:44:09,679
[SPEAKER_01] A vidiš, češće, kao da sam ja kod tebe u live,

1326
00:44:09,679 --> 00:44:10,440
[SPEAKER_01] a ne ti kod mene.

1327
00:44:10,440 --> 00:44:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] Meni paše, meni paše.

1328
00:44:13,599 --> 00:44:17,280
[SPEAKER_01] Baš mi je drago da smo danas

1329
00:44:17,280 --> 00:44:19,460
[SPEAKER_01] na ovakav način razgovarali.

1330
00:44:19,460 --> 00:44:23,119
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, i Bernarda kaže da ova stranica,

1331
00:44:23,500 --> 00:44:28,360
[SPEAKER_01] muževni budite je odličan post koji je svake prve srijede

1332
00:44:28,360 --> 00:44:29,820
[SPEAKER_01] i jako je djelotvoran.

1333
00:44:29,820 --> 00:44:31,699
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, evo vidiš, ovo je veće svjedočanstvo.

1334
00:44:31,699 --> 00:44:33,239
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da, da.

1335
00:44:33,239 --> 00:44:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je svjedočanstvo.

1336
00:44:34,420 --> 00:44:37,159
[SPEAKER_01] Bernarda, javi se tamo u inbox stranice.

1337
00:44:37,840 --> 00:44:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] Svakako zapratite i muževni budite, pratite portal,

1338
00:44:41,340 --> 00:44:46,099
[SPEAKER_01] pratite sve one dobre stvari koje će se tamo još događati.

1339
00:44:46,099 --> 00:44:49,059
[SPEAKER_01] I daj kruno, molim te, najavi nam, odnosno pokaži nam.

1340
00:44:49,059 --> 00:44:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ti je negdje u blizini, odi po nju,

1341
00:44:52,019 --> 00:44:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] predstavi nam knjigu koju si, jedno remek dijelo,

1342
00:44:56,380 --> 00:44:59,019
[SPEAKER_01] prvi prijevod u Hrvatskoj.

1343
00:44:59,019 --> 00:45:01,820
[SPEAKER_01] Svakako moramo to spomenuti, tu knjigu.

1344
00:45:01,820 --> 00:45:05,059
[SPEAKER_01] I malo nam o toj knjizi reci i onda ćeš nam oditi završenu molitvu

1345
00:45:05,059 --> 00:45:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] i na taj način ćemo se večera srastati.

1346
00:45:07,019 --> 00:45:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] Možda, možda.

1347
00:45:08,599 --> 00:45:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, me treba vam ići po nju.

1348
00:45:09,940 --> 00:45:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je, opet, prebremjena je

1349
00:45:12,099 --> 00:45:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] taj se o knjizi Brak o tajstvo vjerne ljubavi.

1350
00:45:15,119 --> 00:45:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je knjiga koju smo preveli s lopovog projekta,

1351
00:45:18,239 --> 00:45:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] objavili.

1352
00:45:19,699 --> 00:45:21,699
[SPEAKER_00] Izašla je prije mjesec dana, otprilike.

1353
00:45:21,699 --> 00:45:26,639
[SPEAKER_00] To je dijelo jednog katoličkog mislilaca, filozofa,

1354
00:45:26,639 --> 00:45:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji je tu dao svoje promišljenje o braku.

1355
00:45:30,039 --> 00:45:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] On je to napisao prije 90 godina na Jemačkom

1356
00:45:33,179 --> 00:45:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] i tek je ove, to je s prošlo godine,

1357
00:45:35,940 --> 00:45:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] nakon 90 godina, to dijelo prevedeno na hrvatski jezik.

1358
00:45:40,139 --> 00:45:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, Bogu, hvala i slava.

1359
00:45:41,260 --> 00:45:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ga.

1360
00:45:42,199 --> 00:45:44,139
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, ako ste izinteresirani,

1361
00:45:44,139 --> 00:45:47,559
[SPEAKER_00] možete javiti se na naš profil

1362
00:45:47,559 --> 00:45:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] ili u strani svakot ili slično,

1363
00:45:49,440 --> 00:45:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] nabaviti tu knjigu.

1364
00:45:51,179 --> 00:45:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je prva knjiga

1365
00:45:53,880 --> 00:45:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] u mislu koju planiramo,

1366
00:45:55,519 --> 00:45:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] koju smo preveli,

1367
00:45:56,519 --> 00:45:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] koju mislimo prevojiti i objaviti.

1368
00:45:59,039 --> 00:46:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ima jako velik tu izbor

1369
00:46:01,300 --> 00:46:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] što možemo napraviti.

1370
00:46:03,179 --> 00:46:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] I evo, svi koju su naručili,

1371
00:46:06,039 --> 00:46:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] koju su nabavili ovu knjigu,

1372
00:46:07,380 --> 00:46:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] su o duševini,

1373
00:46:08,119 --> 00:46:09,300
[SPEAKER_00] zbiljeni progovara.

1374
00:46:09,300 --> 00:46:10,780
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je da potičem sve vas

1375
00:46:10,780 --> 00:46:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji ste zainteresirani,

1376
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:13,639
[SPEAKER_00] da je to saznite mnogo više,

1377
00:46:13,639 --> 00:46:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] još više o braku samom,

1378
00:46:15,559 --> 00:46:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] a i o samom autoru,

1379
00:46:17,340 --> 00:46:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] evo, koji je jako značajan po tome,

1380
00:46:19,659 --> 00:46:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] što, dakle, njega je čak i Hitler progonio,

1381
00:46:22,860 --> 00:46:26,559
[SPEAKER_00] jer je odvažio se pisati protiv Hitlera,

1382
00:46:26,559 --> 00:46:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] i naravno ovaj ga je progonio,

1383
00:46:28,519 --> 00:46:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] ali uspio mu je izbeći.

1384
00:46:30,219 --> 00:46:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da možete misliti

1385
00:46:31,320 --> 00:46:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] kolika je snažna riječ tog autora,

1386
00:46:33,599 --> 00:46:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] od kojeg su se i Hitleru tresle gače.

1387
00:46:37,239 --> 00:46:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, eto, možete...

1388
00:46:40,079 --> 00:46:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam nabavio knjigu,

1389
00:46:41,619 --> 00:46:43,139
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam nabavio knjigu,

1390
00:46:43,139 --> 00:46:44,619
[SPEAKER_01] Kruno, još ti ju nisam platio,

1391
00:46:44,619 --> 00:46:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] čoče u lajvu sad ti to priznaje,

1392
00:46:46,579 --> 00:46:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali svakako,

1393
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:51,420
[SPEAKER_01] ovih dana ću to napraviti,

1394
00:46:51,420 --> 00:46:52,599
[SPEAKER_01] ali nemoj,

1395
00:46:52,599 --> 00:46:54,500
[SPEAKER_01] molim te da ne budeš skroman,

1396
00:46:54,500 --> 00:46:57,739
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne želim da to ostane tako nepokriveno,

1397
00:46:57,739 --> 00:46:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] knjigu si preveo ti,

1398
00:46:59,420 --> 00:47:01,239
[SPEAKER_01] i ti si, ti si u biti zaslužan,

1399
00:47:01,239 --> 00:47:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] što je knjiga na našem hrvatskom tržištu,

1400
00:47:04,559 --> 00:47:05,519
[SPEAKER_01] na hrvatskom jeziku,

1401
00:47:05,519 --> 00:47:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] ti si ju prevodio.

1402
00:47:07,960 --> 00:47:10,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, dobro, možemo to naravno reći.

1403
00:47:10,400 --> 00:47:13,239
[SPEAKER_00] Moj prijatelj Filip,

1404
00:47:13,239 --> 00:47:16,059
[SPEAKER_00] koji je suradnik na portalu u ovom projektu,

1405
00:47:16,059 --> 00:47:17,400
[SPEAKER_00] on mi je ukazao na nju.

1406
00:47:17,400 --> 00:47:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, nije bilo njega,

1407
00:47:18,739 --> 00:47:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja ne bih saznalo za tu knjigu

1408
00:47:20,300 --> 00:47:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] i ne bih vidio da jedno takvo vreme i djelo

1409
00:47:22,940 --> 00:47:26,280
[SPEAKER_00] nije uopće ugledalo svjetlo dana na hrvatskom jeziku.

1410
00:47:26,280 --> 00:47:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, zasluge moraju ići naravno i...

1411
00:47:29,039 --> 00:47:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] I Filipu, i Filipu, svakako.

1412
00:47:30,699 --> 00:47:31,780
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdravimo Filipa,

1413
00:47:31,780 --> 00:47:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] ako nas gleda ili ako će već gledati

1414
00:47:35,059 --> 00:47:37,260
[SPEAKER_01] kroz vidućih 24 sata na portalu.

1415
00:47:37,960 --> 00:47:40,280
[SPEAKER_01] Kruno, hvala ti.

1416
00:47:40,280 --> 00:47:42,199
[SPEAKER_01] Hajdemo zaključiti s molitvom.

1417
00:47:42,199 --> 00:47:45,199
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ti vodi molitvu

1418
00:47:45,199 --> 00:47:47,280
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem će smjeru ići.

1419
00:47:47,280 --> 00:47:48,559
[SPEAKER_01] Prepuštam ti.

1420
00:47:48,559 --> 00:47:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] Prepuštam se u tvoje Bože ruke.

1421
00:47:51,599 --> 00:47:52,719
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo.

1422
00:47:52,820 --> 00:47:54,519
[SPEAKER_00] Neka Duh Sveti bodi Bože.

1423
00:47:54,519 --> 00:47:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] Umej Otca, Sina i Duha Svetoga.

1424
00:47:58,440 --> 00:47:58,800
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

1425
00:47:58,800 --> 00:47:59,260
[SPEAKER_01] Amen.

1426
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodine Otce,

1427
00:48:02,000 --> 00:48:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti na ovoj prilici.

1428
00:48:04,019 --> 00:48:07,239
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, Otce, hvala ti na ovom projektu.

1429
00:48:07,239 --> 00:48:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti na Josipu.

1430
00:48:09,119 --> 00:48:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti na svima koji su pratili

1431
00:48:11,000 --> 00:48:13,239
[SPEAKER_00] ili će pratiti ovaj...

1432
00:48:13,239 --> 00:48:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] To je spogledati ovaj video.

1433
00:48:15,840 --> 00:48:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] Molim te, blagoslovi svaku mušku,

1434
00:48:18,579 --> 00:48:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] osobu pogotovo koja će ovo gledati.

1435
00:48:21,340 --> 00:48:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] Molim te, dotakni svakog muškarca.

1436
00:48:24,880 --> 00:48:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ispuni ga svim potrebnim milostima

1437
00:48:28,099 --> 00:48:29,780
[SPEAKER_00] da može služiti tebi,

1438
00:48:29,780 --> 00:48:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] služiti tvojme kraljestvu,

1439
00:48:32,840 --> 00:48:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] da bude tvoj i Kristof vojnik na ovoj zemlji.

1440
00:48:37,519 --> 00:48:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] Molim te, Otce, za obnovu muženosti,

1441
00:48:44,199 --> 00:48:46,340
[SPEAKER_00] obnovu ženstvenosti,

1442
00:48:46,340 --> 00:48:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] molim te, za obnovu obitelji,

1443
00:48:48,960 --> 00:48:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] molim te, za nove katoličke obitelji

1444
00:48:53,599 --> 00:48:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] koje će preobraziti naše gradove,

1445
00:48:56,699 --> 00:48:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] preobraziti naše društvo,

1446
00:48:58,039 --> 00:49:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] a na kraju preobraziti cijelu našu zemlju.

1447
00:49:01,860 --> 00:49:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] Molim te, za pobjedu,

1448
00:49:04,360 --> 00:49:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] pobjedu Kristova srca i Marijina srca,

1449
00:49:09,079 --> 00:49:13,219
[SPEAKER_00] molim te, za čistoću u muškom srcu,

1450
00:49:13,219 --> 00:49:14,179
[SPEAKER_00] u ženskom srcu,

1451
00:49:14,179 --> 00:49:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] molim te, za sve blagoslove,

1452
00:49:18,000 --> 00:49:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] sve potrebne milosti koje nam želiš dati,

1453
00:49:21,280 --> 00:49:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] da bismo izborili još jednu pobjedu,

1454
00:49:23,699 --> 00:49:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] još jednu Božu pobjedu.

1455
00:49:25,400 --> 00:49:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] To te, molim po Kristu, gospodinu našemu.

1456
00:49:28,480 --> 00:49:29,360
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

1457
00:49:30,039 --> 00:49:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] Slava Otcu i Sinu i Duhu Svetomu,

1458
00:49:33,500 --> 00:49:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi ja še na početku,

1459
00:49:34,820 --> 00:49:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] tako i sada i vas,

1460
00:49:35,960 --> 00:49:37,139
[SPEAKER_00] da i u vijeke, vijekova.

1461
00:49:37,139 --> 00:49:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] Amen.

1462
00:49:37,500 --> 00:49:43,659
[SPEAKER_01] Kruno, hvala ti,

1463
00:49:43,659 --> 00:49:46,119
[SPEAKER_01] laka ti blagoslavljena noć,

1464
00:49:46,119 --> 00:49:49,480
[SPEAKER_01] kao i svima vama koji ste pratili,

1465
00:49:49,480 --> 00:49:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] koji ste odnam pisali,

1466
00:49:51,960 --> 00:49:53,440
[SPEAKER_01] koji ste se uključili,

1467
00:49:53,440 --> 00:49:54,420
[SPEAKER_01] na bilo koji način,

1468
00:49:54,500 --> 00:49:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] otvorimo mogućnost da nam se javite u inbox

1469
00:49:57,559 --> 00:49:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] i id kruni,

1470
00:49:58,960 --> 00:50:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] kroz muževni budite

1471
00:50:00,079 --> 00:50:01,920
[SPEAKER_01] i nama upravo ljubav čeka.

1472
00:50:01,920 --> 00:50:04,420
[SPEAKER_01] Nas sutra čeka novi live,

1473
00:50:04,420 --> 00:50:05,820
[SPEAKER_01] nadamo se,

1474
00:50:05,820 --> 00:50:07,179
[SPEAKER_01] ako vas supluga ne rodi,

1475
00:50:07,179 --> 00:50:12,139
[SPEAKER_01] sutra ćemo malo više govoriti

1476
00:50:12,139 --> 00:50:12,900
[SPEAKER_01] o braku,

1477
00:50:12,900 --> 00:50:15,199
[SPEAKER_01] o predbračnoj i bračnoj čistoći.

1478
00:50:15,559 --> 00:50:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo Kruno i tebe pozivam

1479
00:50:17,000 --> 00:50:19,840
[SPEAKER_01] da se svakako priključiš sutra u live-u

1480
00:50:19,840 --> 00:50:21,659
[SPEAKER_01] i da pratiš.

1481
00:50:21,659 --> 00:50:24,199
[SPEAKER_01] Biće nam gosti jedan bračni par

1482
00:50:24,199 --> 00:50:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] koji ćemo najaviti u storijima,

1483
00:50:25,599 --> 00:50:27,719
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda vidimo se već sutra.

1484
00:50:27,719 --> 00:50:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] Zbogom svako ti dobro,

1485
00:50:29,800 --> 00:50:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] pozdrav tebi Matej.

1486
00:50:31,039 --> 00:50:35,179
[SPEAKER_01] I Bog ti blagoslovio,

1487
00:50:35,179 --> 00:50:35,840
[SPEAKER_01] čujemo se.

1488
00:50:35,840 --> 00:50:36,699
[SPEAKER_01] Laka ti noć.

1489
00:50:36,699 --> 00:50:37,119
[SPEAKER_01] Čujemo se.

1490
00:50:37,119 --> 00:50:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] Laku noć.

1491
